This file contains a collection of photos and videos showcasing the development and functionality of the Autonomous Truck Vision System. 
It includes media demonstrating STOP sign detection, distance measurement with the ultrasonic sensor, motor control using the H-bridge, 
and the integration with the iOS app for real-time monitoring.
